strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"17478","referenceCode":"19N.1.SL.TZ0.S_5a","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Show that the discriminant of f ′ ( x ) is k 2 − 16 .","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 2—Functions","Topic 2—Functions","SL 2.7—Solutions of quadratic equations and inequalities, discriminant and nature of roots"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}